caption.title: Protein interaction map for the 5 cysticercus cultures that matched with the Taenia solium secretome (culture 1 (C1), culture 2 (C2), culture 3 (C3), culture 4 (C4) and culture 5 (C5)).
caption.p: The graph was created with the bioinformatics tool Calculate and Draw Custom Venn diagrams ( http://bioinformatics.psb.ugent.be/webtools/Venn/).
